            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-7ce37595-1400-4231-8aa8-46c14b16ce71">
                Mr. Wragg
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7ce37595-1400-4231-8aa8-46c14b16ce71" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
